      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">29.401-1</ph> Indefinite-delivery contracts for leased equipment.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d1888e8" class="- topic/p ">Insert the clause at <xref href="52.229-1.dita#FAR_52_229_1"
                  base="i1051445"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "/>, State and Local Taxes, in solicitations and contracts for leased equipment when-</p>
         <ol id="d1858e22" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1881e15">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            A fixed-price indefinite-delivery contract is contemplated;</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1881e20">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            The contract will be performed wholly or partly in the United States or its outlying areas; and</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1881e25">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
						            The place or places of delivery are not known at the time of contracting.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
